@startuml 2D_Tenant_Billing_Branding_Domain
title 2-D · Tenant Billing, Branding & Domain Settings (UC-T33 to UC-T38)

start
|Tenant Admin (Owner/Billing)|
:Open Billing & Settings;

|System|
:Verify tenant status = ACTIVE;
:Check role permission\n(Owner or Billing for billing actions);

|Tenant Admin (Owner/Billing)|
if (Admin action?) then (View Current Plan)
  |System|
  :Load current TenantSubscription,\nplan features and renewal date;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Request Plan Upgrade)
  :Select target plan;
  |System|
  :Validate plan eligibility;
  :Create upgrade request or payment session;
  :Notify platform billing workflow if approval needed;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Update Payment Method)
  :Enter or choose payment method;
  |System|
  :Tokenize payment method through provider;
  :Update tenant billing profile;
elseif (Admin action?) then (View Invoices)
  |System|
  :Load tenant invoices and payment status;
else (Configure Branding / Custom Domain)
  |Tenant Admin (Owner)|
  :Update logo, brand colors,\nfavicon or custom domain;
  |System|
  :Validate branding assets and domain format;
  if (Custom domain provided?) then (Yes)
    :Generate DNS verification record;
    |Tenant Admin (Owner)|
    :Configure DNS at domain provider;
    |System|
    :Verify DNS and SSL readiness;
    if (Verification passed?) then (No)
      :Keep domain pending verification;
      stop
    else (Yes)
      :Activate custom domain for tenant;
    endif
  else (No)
    :Save tenant branding configuration;
  endif
endif

|System|
:Invalidate tenant branding/settings cache;
stop
@enduml
